author: Play On Tabletop
description:
Angron and the World Eaters look to break the indomitable will of the Astra Militarum.  Nick brings a Mechanised Assault detachment with five transports and a Storm Lord. Will the World Eaters piloted by Jordan be able to catch the speed of the Militarum or will they get shot up before they get to strike?

The battlefield is brought to you by Titan's Terrain by our good friends over at Tabletop Titans. https://www.tabletoptitans.tv/?ref=PLAYONTABLETOP
